<h3 id="nordlig-vinter">Nordlig Vinter‚Äô</h3>

<p>Nordlig Vinter is a suite of compositions for percussion and iOS devices created by Charles Martin while living in Pite√•, near the Arctic circle in northern Sweden from 2011 to 2012. Harshly cut field recordings reflect the dry, icy environment while minimal jazz inspired melodies on vibraphone and marimba evoke the quiet beauty of such a strange place.</p>

